nd Greenbrier Valley Railroad.', 'Shenandoah Valley Railroad | Shenandoah Valley Railroad refers to one of several railroads in the U.S. state of Virginia:'], 'question': 'The Shenandoah Valley Railroad had considerably backing from another railroad with what nickname?', 'reasoning': 'The context mentions that the Shenandoah Valley Railroad (1867–90) had considerable backing from the Pennsylvania Railroad. The Pennsylvania Railroad is often referred to by its nickname, "Pennsy."', 'search_query': 'What is the nickname of the Pennsylvania Railroad?'}) (input_keys=None), Example({'augmented': True, 'context': ['Dustin Kensrue | Dustin Michael Kensrue (pronounced KENZ-roo) (born November 18, 1980) is a vocalist, lyricist, and rhythm guitarist in the Orange County, California, post-hardcore/experimental rock quartet Thrice, as well as a solo artist.', 'Jimmy Urine | James Euringer (born September 7, 1969), known professionally as Jimmy Urine, is an American singer, songwriter, and musician. He is best known as the lead singer and programmer of electropunk band Mindless Self Indulgence.', 'Thrice | Thrice is an American rock band from Irvine, California, formed in 1998. The group was founded by guitarist/vocalist Dustin Kensrue and guitarist Teppei Teranishi while they were in high school.'], 'question': 'What occupation do Dustin Kensrue and Jimmy Urine share?', 'reasoning': 'Both Dustin Kensrue and Jimmy Urine are described as singers in the given context. Dustin Kensrue is a vocalist in the band Thrice, and Jimmy Urine is the lead singer of the band Mindless Self Indulgence. Therefore, the shared occupation is singer.', 'search_query': 'What is the shared occupation of Dustin Kensrue and Jimmy Urine based on the given context?'}) (input_keys=None)]

